quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Sumber : CIAYO Comics\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Sumber : CIAYO Comics&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/bpr2-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/bpr2.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-45347\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/bpr2.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber : CIAYO Comics\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/bpr2.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/bpr2-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-45347\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber : CIAYO Comics</p></div></p>\n<p>Terkadang dalam sebuah hubungan, kalian nggak harus menjadi matahari ataupun pelangi untuk orang yang kamu sayang kok. Mungkin nggak mudah untuk bisa membuat seseorang selalu bahagia dan tersenyum. Tapi, setidaknya kamu bisa selalu ada buat dia saat dibutuhkan atau minimal gak nyakitin. Simple kan?</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_45345\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-45345\" data-attachment-id=\"45345\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/hati-hati-dibuat-baper-baca-komik-ini/attachment/bpr/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/bpr.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;